author: gstein
msg: Handle the last-changed information better.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/wc-metadata.sql:
(*.changed_*): update comments in the schema to note that we may not
have changed_date and/or changed_author since those revprops could be
deleted.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/entries.c:
(read_entries): no longer special-case cmd_rev==0 since that can
actually be true for an empty, initial repository.
(insert_base_node): bind each changed_* column individually based on
whether we have the associated piece of information.
(insert_working_node): bind each changed* column individually
(write_entry): don't special-case changed_author. it is legal for it to
be missing.
